            The 3rd International Conference IEEE SITIS 2007=20
               		 December 16-19 2007=20
                	     Jiangong Jinjiang Hotel=20
                 	        Shanghai, China=20
               	(in cooperation with ACM Sigapp.fr)
               	  http://www.u-bourgogne.fr/sitis
